      "status": "Informational",
      "details": "Document OCR processing logs include extracted text snippets for debugging purposes. Some snippets may contain PII from insurance documents (names, policy numbers, SSNs). While the retention period is compliant, the PII content in log entries may create a data minimization concern. Recommendation: implement PII redaction in log output."
    }
